          <h5 class='title'>Test</h5>
          <ol>
            <li>Your application uses the same rendering and JavaScript engine as the Project Spartan browser so most of your testing can be done on your website and in the browser.</li>
            <li>To test your application on a device download the ManifoldJS test harness from the store and follow the directions.  Coming soon!</li>
            <li>To test locally, in the folder for your app, type "ManifoldJS run windows"
            <ul>
