            </ul>
            </li>
          </ol>

          <h5 class='title'>Build</h5>
          <p><strong>With Visual Studio</strong></p>

          <ol>
            <li>Download and install Visual Studio (community edition works fine) and open the source code folder.</li>
            <li>Open the Project in Visual Studio</li>
            <li>Use the store commands from Visual Studio to create the app package.</li>
          </ol>

          <strong>With the Windows 10 SDK</strong>
          <ol>
            <li>Download the [Windows10 SKD] (http://dev.windows.com/en-US/windows-10-developer-preview-tools) (must be running Windows 10 Technical preview)</li>
            <li>Build with [these instructions] (https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/hh446767(v=vs.85).aspx) for MakeAppX.</li>
            <li>Submit to Store</li>
          </ol>
